<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>ETYM</title>
    <!-- Google Icon Fonts used by Materialize -->
    <link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Alegreya+Sans+SC&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Materialize CSS Framework -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/css/materialize.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/style.css" />
    <!-- JavaScript for Materialize -->
    <script defer src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/js/materialize.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="navbar-fixed">
        <nav class="light-green darken-2">
            <div class="nav-wrapper">
                <ul class="right">
                    <li>
                        <% if (user) { %>
                        <a href="/logout"><i class="material-icons left">trending_flat</i>Log Out</a>
                        <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/auth/google"><i class="material-icons left">vpn_key</i>Login with Google</a>
                        <% } %>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <h3>Welcome to <%= title %></h3>
    </div>

    <div class="parallax-container">
        <div class="parallax">
            <img src="images/books.jpg" alt="" class="responsive-img">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h5>ETYM is a place where you can learn the etymology of commonly used words.</h5>
    </div>

    <p>The word 'etymology' itself means the study of the history of words. The root of the word 'etymology' comes from
        the Greek 'etumon' which means "true sense." </p>

    <div class="parallax-container">
        <div class="parallax">
            <img src="images/openbooks.jpg" alt="" class="responsive-img">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col s12 m4">
                    <div class="icon-block">
                        <h2 class="center green-text">
                            <i class="medium material-icons">all_inclusive</i>
                        </h2>
                        <h5 class="center">Learn where words come from</h5>
                        <p class="light">Learning word etymologies changes your perspective on the meaning of words and
                            why we use them, creating a deeper awareness of the reality we manifest collectively based
                            on what words we choose to use regularly. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col s12 m4">
                    <div class="icon-block">
                        <h2 class="center green-text">
                            <i class="medium material-icons">group</i>
                        </h2>
                        <h5 class="center">View other users lists</h5>
                        <p class="light">Continue to grow and expand on your knowledge base by being able to see what
                            other users are researching. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col s12 m4">
                    <div class="icon-block">
                        <h2 class="center green-text">
                            <i class=" medium material-icons">details</i>
                        </h2>
                        <h5 class="center">Save to your unique list</h5>
                        <p class="light">Add words and origins to your list whenever you learn them, and save them so
                            that you can view your progress over time, and review any words and origins that you forget.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="center"><a href="/auth/google">
            <button type="submit">Login to learn more!</button></a>
    </div>


    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.1.1.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/materialize.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $('.parallax').parallax();
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>